      <title>Android手机使用Jupyter写程序</title>
      <link href="/2020/08/04/Android%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Jupyter%E5%86%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F/"/>
      <url>/2020/08/04/Android%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Jupyter%E5%86%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><code>注：建议先看文章底部的扩展</code></p><h3 id="安装条件"><a href="#安装条件" class="headerlink" title="安装条件"></a>安装条件</h3><p>Android 7.0以上操作系统<br>存储容量32G以上</p><h3 id="安装Termux"><a href="#安装Termux" class="headerlink" title="安装Termux"></a>安装Termux</h3><p>下载地址：<a href="https://www.baidu.com/">点我</a></p><h3 id="安装环境"><a href="#安装环境" class="headerlink" title="安装环境"></a>安装环境</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkg <span class="keyword">in</span> clang python fftw libzmq -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等进度走完，有点慢，建议用移动数据或坐在100M以上带宽的WiFi路由器旁边</p><h3 id="检查是否安装完成"><a href="#检查是否安装完成" class="headerlink" title="检查是否安装完成"></a>检查是否安装完成</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python --version</span><br><span class="line">pip --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="升级pip"><a href="#升级pip" class="headerlink" title="升级pip"></a>升级<code>pip</code></h3><p>可以通过 <code>pip --version</code> 查看pip的版本<br>必须要20.1版本才能正常安装jupyter<br>所以低于20.1的要升级</p><p>输入下面的命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install --upgrade pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再次检查pip版本为20.1就可以开始下一步操作了</p><h3 id="安装-Jupyter"><a href="#安装-Jupyter" class="headerlink" title="安装 Jupyter"></a>安装 <code>Jupyter</code></h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install jupyter</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>没报错就说明安装好了</p><h3 id="启动-Jupyter"><a href="#启动-Jupyter" class="headerlink" title="启动 Jupyter"></a>启动 Jupyter</h3><p>把语言修改为简体中文</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> LANG=<span class="string">&quot;zh_CN.UTF-8&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行Jupyter</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">jupyter notebook</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到，有个URL<br>你可以去复制它后面的token<br>例如：?token=bdb199c5587f5fab07643afa96<br><code>=</code>后面的就是token值了<br>长按复制这串值（不是复制这里的，是复制Termux里的）</p><h3 id="登录-Jupyter"><a href="#登录-Jupyter" class="headerlink" title="登录 Jupyter"></a>登录 Jupyter</h3><p>打开浏览器（这里推荐使用Chrome）<br>用浏览器打开<br>输入链接 <code>http://localhost:8888/</code> 打开<code>Jupyter</code></p><p>在最下面的<code>token</code>栏中把前面复制的token粘贴进去<br>然后在下面的输入框输入你想要设置的密码<br>下次打开Jupyter的时候要输入这个密码才能进入</p><h4 id="最后至于Jupyter怎么用，自行百度，我只能帮你到这里了"><a href="#最后至于Jupyter怎么用，自行百度，我只能帮你到这里了" class="headerlink" title="最后至于Jupyter怎么用，自行百度，我只能帮你到这里了"></a>最后至于Jupyter怎么用，自行百度，我只能帮你到这里了</h4><h2 id="扩展"><a href="#扩展" class="headerlink" title="扩展"></a>扩展</h2><h3 id="修改Termux快捷键"><a href="#修改Termux快捷键" class="headerlink" title="修改Termux快捷键"></a>修改Termux快捷键</h3><p>快捷键默认只有1排，我们把它修改成3排</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir <span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.termux</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;extra-keys = [[&#x27;ESC&#x27;,&#x27;/&#x27;,&#x27;-&#x27;,&#x27;HOME&#x27;,&#x27;UP&#x27;,&#x27;END&#x27;,&#x27;PGUP&#x27;,&#x27;&lt;&#x27;,&#x27;&gt;&#x27;],[&#x27;TAB&#x27;,&#x27;CTRL&#x27;,&#x27;ALT&#x27;,&#x27;LEFT&#x27;,&#x27;DOWN&#x27;,&#x27;RIGHT&#x27;,&#x27;PGDN&#x27;,&#x27;[&#x27;,&#x27;]&#x27;],[&#x27;$&#x27;,&#x27;QUOTE&#x27;,&#x27;=&#x27;,&#x27;&#123;&#x27;,&#x27;&#125;&#x27;,&#x27;(&#x27;,&#x27;)&#x27;,&#x27;&amp;&#x27;,&#x27;%&#x27;]]&quot;</span> &gt; <span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.termux/termux.properties</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>重启</code>Termux即可</p><h3 id="切换到国内源"><a href="#切换到国内源" class="headerlink" title="切换到国内源"></a>切换到国内源</h3><p>在步骤 <code>安装环境</code> 的时候出错或者下载速度慢的话<br>可以试着切换到<code>清华大学</code>的<code>Termux</code>源</p><p>命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sed -i <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*stable main\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/termux-packages-24 stable main@&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br><span class="line">sed -i <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*games stable\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/game-packages-24 games stable@&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/game.list</span><br><span class="line">sed -i <span class="string">&#x27;s@^\(deb.*science stable\)$@#\1\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux/science-packages-24 science stable@&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$PREFIX</span>/etc/apt/sources.list.d/science.list</span><br><span class="line">apt update &amp;&amp; apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="修改pip源"><a href="#修改pip源" class="headerlink" title="修改pip源"></a>修改<code>pip</code>源</h3><p>国内直接<code>pip install</code>命令安装程序可能会出现报错<br>我们只需要<code>pip</code>的源换到国内就好了<br>命令如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir <span class="variable">$HOEM</span>/.pip</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;[global]\ntimeout = 6000\nindex-url = https://mirrors.163.com/pypi/simple/\ntrusted-host = mirrors.163.com&quot;</span> &gt; <span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.pip/pip.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
